Commission for Metrohunter featuring TheLupineOne!

Looks like Ralf discovered a scroll that will let him and Tuli learn kung fu really quick! But changes quickly start to overtake both of them while Tuli examines the find. Looks like they'll be getting into martial arts very quick, indeed! After all, why waste time learning when you can just become characters that already know self-defense! Also, the scroll burnt up, so it doesn't look like they'll be getting out of this situation anytime soon!
